        {
            "title": "A股窄幅靠穩   深股跑輸",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">A股午後窄幅靠穩，深股跑輸，兩市成交合計29654.15億元(人民幣‧下同)。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240307_FI_source-ap_AShare-3.png.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240307_FI_source-ap_AShare-3.png.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">上證綜指全日升11點或0.27%，報4151點，今早以4150點開市，升10點或0.25%，最低見4138點，跌1點或0.02%，尾段升幅擴大，最高見4170點，升31點或0.75%，全日成交13655.26億元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">深證成指全日升12點或0.09%，報14342點，今早開市報14371點，亦升42點或0.29%，上午低見14234，跌95點或0.66%，為全日低位，午後走勢好轉，最高見14411，升82點或0.57%，為全日高位，全日成交15998.84億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">滬深300指數全日升12點或0.26%，報4717點，今早升19點或0.42%，開報4725點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">創業板指數全日跌19點或0.57%，報3323點，今早開市報3359點，升17點或0.51%。</p>\n</div>",
